article_title: GOP Presidential Candidates' Obamacare Repeal Plans Are Also Large Tax Cuts

article_metadata.author: Ryan Ellis

og.description: Earlier this week, Wisconsin governor and 2016 GOP presidential hopeful Scott Walker released his version of an Obamacare "repeal and replace" plan. There's also versions out there from Senator Marco Rubio (R-Florida) and Governor Bobby Jindal (R-La.) There are yet others on Capitol Hill: the Republican Study Committee plan, the plan advanced [...]
